An arcane wrecking ball or sledgehammer projects from your armor. The demolisher has the following traits:
	• Weapon Category: Simple Melee
	• Damage on a Hit: 1d10 Force plus the ability modifier used for the attack roll
	• Properties: Reach
	• If you hit a creature that is at least one size smaller than you with the demolisher, you can:
		• Push the creature up to 10 feet straight away from yourself
		• Pull the creature up to 10 feet toward yourself

Giant Stature (Bonus):
As a Bonus Action, you transform and enlarge your armor for 1 minute. For the duration, the following is true:
	• Your reach increases by 5 feet
	• If you are smaller than Large, you become Large, along with anything you are wearing. If there isn't enough room for you to increase your size, your size doesn't change.
	• You can use this Bonus Action a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.
	
